          <p><img src="/conferences/2007conference/speakers/CharlesBowen.jpg" alt="Charles Bowen, United Kingdom" width="134" height="156" hspace="10" align="left" />Charles Bowen took over as Executive Director of the International Association of Oil and Gas Producers in February 2005, after a 30-year career with TOTAL. He spent his early career in development projects, and then moved into production management, HSE management and then general management.</p>
