          <p><img src="/conferences/2007conference/speakers/LeeHunt.jpg" alt="Dr. Lee Hunt, USA" width="134" height="156" hspace="10" align="left" />Dr. Lee Hunt serves as the Chief Executive of IADC, responsible for managing IADC's worldwide operations. Before being named President in 1990, his prior Association positions included Manager for State Government Affairs, Environmental Affairs and Human Resources. Dr. Hunt holds a PhD in political science from Northwestern University and received his law degree from South Texas College of Law.</p>
