          <p><img src="/conferences/2007conference/speakers/TadLeBlanc.jpg" alt="Tad LeBlanc, USA" width="134" height="156" hspace="10" align="left" />Tad LeBlanc has worked in the oil and gas industry for over 25 years and has been with Baker Energy in Houston, TX for the past 14 years. Mr. LeBlanc has served in various positions ranging from operations and maintenance to health, safety, environment, and compliance.</p>
          <p>In his current position, Mr. LeBlanc is responsible for the overall management for Baker Energy&rsquo;s Health, Safety, Environment &amp; Compliance Program worldwide. His team ensures compliance with required federal, state, and international regulatory agencies and client contractual obligations. Significant accomplishments while managing the HSE&amp;C Team include:</p>
